Kuroth is a Oeridian power of Theft and Treasure-Finding. A good thief that made powerhood, due in part to the sponsorship of Olidammara. He would have made any Fated or Believer+of+the+Source proud.
Kuroth is best known for the artifact Kuroth's Quill.
Sources: Living Greyhawk Journal #3, Book of Artifacts, DMG1, Dragon #294,
